The People of the State of Illinois, defendant in error, v. John Cannon, plaintiff in error.Gen. No. 33,717.

O’Connor, J., dissents.

Opinion filed January 6, 1930.Jay J. McCarthy and John B. Fruehtl, for plaintiff in error. John A. Swanson, State’s Attorney, for defendant in error; Edward E. Wilson and John Holman, Assistant State’s Attorneys, of counsel. Mr. Justice Matchett

delivered the opinion of the court.
